data.description: Solar heated pool, multiple fruit trees, large corner lot and the cleanest garage around! Not to mention the updates that include kitchen, bathroom, flooring, paint, landscaping, sprinkler system, pool equipment and more. With over 2000' living space this beautiful J&J built 3/2 home has it all. This beautiful home is located in the friendly and desirable neighborhood of Sorrento East, with access to the private marina just minutes away, you really can have it all. A/C and water heater updated in 2007, overhead fixtures updated with a contemporary look, laundry inside and updated, lots of oak tree shade and a sparkling pool for those steamy days and a fireplace for those cooler evenings!
